*******************************************************************************
       Name: Architecture Scan
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_SELF
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 8
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: You no longer perceive structural magical patterns.
Acquisition:
   - Psionicist: level 7
Description:
   Architecture Scan is a psionic detection ability that allows the
   Psionicist to perceive the magical structure of their surroundings and
   any enchantments present. The psionicist extends their mental senses
   to detect the structural patterns of magical constructs, effectively
   granting a form of magical sight similar to detect magic but filtered
   through a psionic framework.

   While Architecture Scan is active, the Psionicist can see magical
   auras on objects, rooms, and characters, and gains additional
   information about the nature and intensity of magical effects they
   encounter. This is the Psionicist's equivalent of the Magi's detect
   magic but derived from mental perception rather than arcane theory.
*******************************************************************************
